	quest.30B5FFC763CBC1E5.quest_subtitle: "Repairs gear"
	quest.30B5FFC763CBC1E5.title: "Tome of Repair"
	quest.30DACF0F1200FFD0.quest_desc: ["The §eSandy Waystone§r is the §baesthetic§r variant perfect for bases in the §6desert§r.", "", "§7•§r Activate it and teleport between it and any other waystone in the network.", "§7•§r Identical function to the standard waystone, only the sandy look differs."]
	quest.30DACF0F1200FFD0.quest_subtitle: "Desert"
	quest.30DACF0F1200FFD0.title: "Sandy Waystone"
	quest.31094F326A7FC887.quest_desc: ["The chamber draws source from surrounding jars to transform items. Everything on the Arcanist's path passes through here.", "", "Here it includes livingwood in the recipe — because living wood channels source better than any other.", "ars_nouveau:imbuement_chamber", "31094F326A7FC887", "640EBD11DF1BA24F", "xp"]
	quest.31094F326A7FC887.quest_subtitle: "Cross-mod — processing hub"
	quest.31094F326A7FC887.title: "Imbuement Chamber"
	quest.311EB32138F7A3A1.quest_desc: ["The Ring of Thor mines a 3x3x1 pattern at once. Combo with a manasteel_pickaxe for advanced mining.", "botania:thor_ring", "311EB32138F7A3A1", "625C707DB379C763", "xp"]
	quest.311EB32138F7A3A1.quest_subtitle: "Mine 3x3 blocks"
	quest.311EB32138F7A3A1.title: "Ring of Thor"
	quest.314CA09B4DF07ECD.quest_desc: ["§eAutomatically feeds§r you using the food stored in the backpack.", "§7•§r Set the filters to choose what can be eaten.", "Never starve in the middle of a dungeon again."]
	quest.314CA09B4DF07ECD.quest_subtitle: "Eats on its own"
	quest.314CA09B4DF07ECD.title: "Upgrade: Feeding"
	quest.31D0547CB8D1E302.quest_desc: ["The mana tablet stores 500k mana. Carry it in your inventory to use with a mana_lens at range, or drain it into a pool.", "botania:mana_tablet", "31D0547CB8D1E302", "5C421A9F42742FEF", "xp"]
	quest.31D0547CB8D1E302.quest_subtitle: "Portable storage"
	quest.31D0547CB8D1E302.title: "Mana Tablet"
	quest.320CE693F4FF644D.quest_desc: ["The mana ring (with mana_pearl) stores mana to power your tools. Equip it in a curio ring slot. Recharges when it touches a pool.", "botania:mana_ring", "320CE693F4FF644D", "5BD53DBAB691BE89", "xp"]
	quest.320CE693F4FF644D.quest_subtitle: "Ring that stores mana"
	quest.320CE693F4FF644D.title: "Mana Ring"
	quest.32E375165DD1FA9C.quest_desc: ["&7&o[Initial Record Recovered: The Age of Utopia]&r", "", "{image:kubejs:textures/static/utopia.png width:200 height:100 align:center}", "", "There was a time, before the ashes, known as the &6Golden Age&r. A unified society, where the &3steam of machines&r danced in harmony with the &3flow of mana&r, and humanity had broken the barrier of the ethereal, sealing pacts with &bancient spirits&r.", "", "But in the shadows of that utopia, an isolated group of visionaries rejected the limits imposed by nature. They lived and breathed for a single goal: the creation of the &5Philosopher's Stone&r.", "", "This artifact was not merely a legend about turning lead into gold; it represented the final &6breaking&r of the laws of the universe. The Stone would grant its bearer &5Perfect Transmutation&r: the ability to create matter from nothing, to generate infinite energy at no cost, and to mold reality itself without suffering the consequences of Equivalent Exchange.", "", "Driven by this ambition to reach the divine, the group operated in a fierce and silent competition. Each member, locked away in their own tower of knowledge, sought to prove that their method was the only path to &5absolute power&r."]
	quest.32E375165DD1FA9C.quest_subtitle: "Where it all began..."
	quest.32E375165DD1FA9C.title: "The Lost Utopia"
	quest.3357E9CD330940DE.quest_subtitle: "§6Centennial Trophy§r"
	quest.3357E9CD330940DE.title: "100 Chests Opened"
	quest.336E7EADEB3E226A.quest_desc: ["The magnet ring pulls in dropped items over a large radius. Equip it in a curio slot. Combine with mob farms.", "botania:magnet_ring", "336E7EADEB3E226A", "302A018EF5873282", "xp"]
	quest.336E7EADEB3E226A.quest_subtitle: "Attracts items"
	quest.336E7EADEB3E226A.title: "Ring of Magnetization"
	quest.33AC8FC4874F9ABC.quest_desc: ["§cCursed Kinetic Core§r is the corrupted, unstable form of the core, spat out raw by the §6Mechanical Crafter§r.", "", "The raw motion hasn't been tamed yet. It must be purified by an Occultism ritual before it can serve."]
	quest.33AC8FC4874F9ABC.title: "Cursed Kinetic Core"
	quest.33CB938095170563.quest_desc: ["Drop §bCharged Certus§r + §credstone§r + §equartz dust§r into water.", "The §dFluix§r is born — the heart of all connections."]
	quest.33CB938095170563.quest_subtitle: "The reaction"
	quest.33CB938095170563.title: "Fluix Crystal"
	quest.33FDEF46BC5C5197.quest_subtitle: "Fiftyfold"
	quest.33FDEF46BC5C5197.title: "50 Chests Opened"
	quest.348896FAB1D5A00B.quest_desc: ["Archwood (cascading, blazing, vexing, flourishing) appears in Ars Nouveau biomes. Each type has a specific effect on nearby creatures.", "ars_nouveau:blue_archwood_log", "348896FAB1D5A00B", "0D73B8B241F02C18", "xp"]
	quest.348896FAB1D5A00B.quest_subtitle: "Source wood"
	quest.348896FAB1D5A00B.title: "Archwood Logs"
	quest.35161A34CE3747CB.quest_desc: ["Make §e3§r fresh salads from Pam's.", "pamhc2foodextended:berryvinaigrettesaladitem", "35161A34CE3747CB", "389186526F0C5036", "xp_levels"]
	quest.35161A34CE3747CB.quest_subtitle: "13 recipes in Pam's"
	quest.35161A34CE3747CB.title: "Fresh Salads"
	quest.3539EFABFC5B2EF5.quest_desc: ["Here the recipe takes a different path: mechanical_crafting with cogwheel + golden_sheet + §dsource_gem§r (Ars).", "", "The precision mechanism unlocks mid-to-late Create components (mechanical arm, deployer advance, etc). Source_gem ensures the player has gone through Ars Nouveau.", "create:precision_mechanism", "3539EFABFC5B2EF5", "2280EB8C89AA99D0", "xp"]
	quest.3539EFABFC5B2EF5.quest_subtitle: "Intermediate component (cross-mod)"
	quest.3539EFABFC5B2EF5.title: "Precision Mechanism"
	quest.35A21FE8CEE89682.quest_desc: ["Make §e3§r pizzas from Pam's.", "pamhc2foodextended:anchovypepperonipizzaitem", "35A21FE8CEE89682", "230E1CD2F3C82EC0", "xp_levels"]
	quest.35A21FE8CEE89682.quest_subtitle: "6 recipes in Pam's"
	quest.35A21FE8CEE89682.title: "Pizzeria"
	quest.35E9E6C9E993847D.quest_desc: ["Make §e5§r pies from Pam's.", "pamhc2foodextended:apricotpieitem", "35E9E6C9E993847D", "0D3677ACC655A730", "xp_levels"]
	quest.35E9E6C9E993847D.quest_subtitle: "54 recipes in Pam's"
	quest.35E9E6C9E993847D.title: "Pastry Chef — Pies"
	quest.361F4B76C4882401.quest_desc: ["Obtain a §6scroll_fire§r and activate it to learn spells from this school.", "", "§7Scrolls are generated in structures, bought from wandering traders, or dropped by mages."]
	quest.361F4B76C4882401.quest_subtitle: "Fireball, Burning Dash, Magma Bomb"
	quest.361F4B76C4882401.title: "School of Fire"
	quest.363C36DBD3BC5F8D.quest_desc: ["Venture into the §ejungle§r to find lush §6wild gardens§r.", "", "The dense vegetation hides tufts full of tropical fruits and spices.", "Break them §7•§r and expand your pantry with exotic flavors."]
	quest.363C36DBD3BC5F8D.title: "Found and broke the garden"
	quest.36D0073E0AC82656.quest_desc: ["The apparatus is the crafting core of the veteran Arcanist. Tomes, parchments, advanced items — all are born here.", "", "To assemble it, you need a §dKinetic Core§r — mechanics and magic meet at this point.", "ars_nouveau:enchanting_apparatus", "36D0073E0AC82656", "7E3336D920A0B98E", "xp"]
	quest.36D0073E0AC82656.quest_subtitle: "F2 requirement — arcane crafting"
	quest.36D0073E0AC82656.title: "Enchanting Apparatus"
	quest.37612FAA4E2B0097.quest_desc: ["Hydra Hill in the Twilight. Heads regenerate, small dragons. Good prep for the Ender Dragon.", "", "§eReward:§r 55 XP levels + boss trophy"]
	quest.37612FAA4E2B0097.quest_subtitle: "Three heads, three terrors"
	quest.37612FAA4E2B0097.title: "Tier 5: Hydra"
	quest.3767F01920B31AAC.quest_desc: ["Locked in his scribe's tower, the &dArcanist&r rejected physical matter. To him, the path to &5Perfect Transmutation&r was the rewriting of reality. Obsessed, he sought to compose the &lPrimordial Glyph&r, draining jars of Source to the last drop to solidify pure magic, in the hope of &lweaving a spell&r of creation that would defy the &6laws of the universe&r."]
	quest.3767F01920B31AAC.quest_subtitle: "The Pursuit"
	quest.3767F01920B31AAC.title: "The Arcanist (Ars Nouveau)"
	quest.37C6978A2F9F2F90.quest_desc: ["Lootr gives an instanced chest §aper player§r — everyone gets loot.", "Open your §efirst§r loot chest."]
	quest.37C6978A2F9F2F90.quest_subtitle: "§2Per-player chests§r"
	quest.37C6978A2F9F2F90.title: "First Chest"
	quest.38559AAC9086747D.quest_desc: ["A spell parchment records a spell for reuse. Use scribes_table → spell_book → parchment.", "ars_nouveau:spell_parchment", "38559AAC9086747D", "07C30FC836E0919D", "xp"]
	quest.38559AAC9086747D.quest_subtitle: "Spell parchment"
	quest.38559AAC9086747D.title: "Spell Parchment"
	quest.39057A5D83FECF13.quest_desc: ["Andesite casing encases most early-to-mid Create machines. Shape: alloy on the edges, log in the center (any wood).", "create:andesite_casing", "39057A5D83FECF13", "00BE8118FF7953A6", "xp"]
	quest.39057A5D83FECF13.quest_subtitle: "Basic casing"
	quest.39057A5D83FECF13.title: "Andesite Casing"
	quest.391FE107A7D08C5D.quest_desc: ["Yeti Lair in the Snowy Forest. Intermediate boss.", "", "§eReward:§r 45 XP levels + drop"]
	quest.391FE107A7D08C5D.quest_subtitle: "King of ice"
	quest.391FE107A7D08C5D.title: "Side: Alpha Yeti"
	quest.3951827CD3324795.quest_desc: ["Wild wixies appear in archwood biomes (rarer). Provide an enchanting_apparatus for automated wixie crafting.", "ars_nouveau:wixie_shards", "3951827CD3324795", "65AD8ADB2AD73DDC", "xp"]
	quest.3951827CD3324795.quest_subtitle: "Drop from wild wixie"
	quest.3951827CD3324795.title: "Wixie Shards"
	quest.39DB897098388FB7.quest_desc: ["Book of binding empty: writable_book tossed into spirit_fire. The base for creating specialized books.", "occultism:book_of_binding_empty", "39DB897098388FB7", "226FB8D93AA335E8", "xp"]
	quest.39DB897098388FB7.quest_subtitle: "Binding base"
	quest.39DB897098388FB7.title: "Book of Binding (Empty)"
	quest.3A027FBA21003761.quest_desc: ["The Wilden Chimera is the boss of Ars Nouveau. Summon it with a wilden horn on the ritual brazier.", "", "Rewards: wings for permanent flight, spike for advanced crafting."]
	quest.3A027FBA21003761.quest_subtitle: "Final boss (Ars)"
	quest.3A027FBA21003761.title: "Wilden Chimera"
	quest.3A74AF74766A2801.quest_subtitle: "Energizing crystals"
	quest.3A74AF74766A2801.title: "Charger"
	quest.3A7667F2D9CD57A3.quest_desc: ["Links multiple chests and barrels into a single access point.", "§7•§r Place the storage blocks against the Controller to unify them.", "Access all the connected stock by opening a single block."]
	quest.3A7667F2D9CD57A3.quest_subtitle: "Links multiple chests"
	quest.3A7667F2D9CD57A3.title: "Storage Controller"
	quest.3ABDCDBB650E1726.quest_desc: ["Craft or obtain the §6Netherite Tome§r. Each tier allows §emore inscribed spells§r and §emore powerful casts§r.", "", "§7Crafting: recipe similar to the base spell book, with the ingredient of the corresponding tier."]
	quest.3ABDCDBB650E1726.quest_subtitle: "Top of the craftable progression"
	quest.3ABDCDBB650E1726.title: "Netherite Tome"
	quest.3ADA15344F5BD416.quest_desc: ["The encased chain drive is a compact version — it combines a shaft + andesite casing. Useful for clean builds.", "create:encased_chain_drive", "3ADA15344F5BD416", "3E84A86536ABE92E", "xp"]
	quest.3ADA15344F5BD416.quest_subtitle: "Chain drive hidden in a block"
	quest.3ADA15344F5BD416.title: "Encased Chain Drive"
	quest.3AE56186A0CA1A30.quest_desc: ["Stabilizer tier 4: djinni ritual + iesnium + spirit_crystal. Adds +2000 slots to the storage_controller. Advanced.", "occultism:storage_stabilizer_tier4", "3AE56186A0CA1A30", "6498FE18668E9DF2", "xp"]
	quest.3AE56186A0CA1A30.quest_subtitle: "Maximum capacity"
	quest.3AE56186A0CA1A30.title: "Storage Stabilizer Tier 4"
	quest.3AEDAFB44EE7F179.quest_desc: ["You did it all. 387,420,489 berries in one slot.", "", "§oYou didn't need this. But you did it anyway.§r"]
	quest.3AEDAFB44EE7F179.quest_subtitle: "Compaction master"
	quest.3AEDAFB44EE7F179.title: "§dSourceberry Sack X9"
	quest.3AF5F89CDE0D5156.quest_desc: ["The §eKinetic Core§r you forged in the previous phase is required again — the progression is truly cross-cutting.", "", "Create's movement enters as the soul of the new Botania crystal."]
	quest.3AF5F89CDE0D5156.title: "Kinetic Core (F2)"
	quest.3BA9C2299B88C42E.quest_desc: ["Smaller drawers, designed for §esmall§r and varied items.", "§7•§r Same idea, but with more divisions and lower capacity per slot.", "Good for organizing small raw materials."]
	quest.3BA9C2299B88C42E.quest_subtitle: "Small items"
	quest.3BA9C2299B88C42E.title: "Half Drawer"
	quest.3BBA4B57171FCE82.quest_desc: ["The terra plate is a multi-block structure that takes ingredients and mana to forge terrasteel. Craft it with 4 livingrock + 1 mana_diamond + 4 manasteel_ingot.", "botania:terra_plate", "3BBA4B57171FCE82", "1910B75593F3C438", "xp"]
	quest.3BBA4B57171FCE82.quest_subtitle: "Terrasteel forge"
	quest.3BBA4B57171FCE82.title: "Terra Plate"
	quest.3BE6BD7EE8F56235.quest_desc: ["§eSpiritual Core§r — the final milestone of this journey. The §dSoul Gem§r and the three previous cores converge into a single stable work.", "", "Create, Botania, Ars and Occultism in one object. It unlocks §bArs§r and Botania's §2Terrasteel§r."]
	quest.3BE6BD7EE8F56235.title: "The Spiritual Core"
	quest.3BFF59F53C1A846E.quest_desc: ["Throw the Cursed Magical Agglutinate into a Mana Pool with at least §b50,000 mana§r.", "", "This is F1's signature item: it unlocks §eCreate§r (andesite_alloy), §eBotania§r (black stone pools), and §eOccultism§r (binding foliot).", "", "Every other mod will require the Agglutinate in its next tiers."]
	quest.3BFF59F53C1A846E.quest_subtitle: "The heart of F1"
	quest.3BFF59F53C1A846E.title: "§6Magical Agglutinate"
	quest.3C17415BAD9B6370.quest_desc: ["Make §e4§r smoothies from Pam's.", "pamhc2foodextended:apricotsmoothieitem", "3C17415BAD9B6370", "5E31ED99FD55459E", "xp_levels"]
	quest.3C17415BAD9B6370.quest_subtitle: "45 recipes in Pam's"
	quest.3C17415BAD9B6370.title: "Smoothies"
	quest.3C4527C189F0544B.quest_desc: ["Lich Tower. Learn to dodge arcane projectiles. Drop: Lich Crown.", "", "§eReward:§r 30 XP levels + boss trophy"]
	quest.3C4527C189F0544B.quest_subtitle: "Magister of the dead"
	quest.3C4527C189F0544B.title: "Tier 2: Lich"
	quest.3C75FD2842D5A444.quest_desc: ["§9BOMD§r adds 4 unique bosses, each in a specific biome:", "", "§7- Gauntlet — Plains/Savanna", "§7- Lich — Snowy biomes", "§7- Obsidilith — End", "§7- Void Blossom — Mushroom Islands", "", "Each one drops a Soul Star — a rare endgame material."]
	quest.3C75FD2842D5A444.quest_subtitle: "4 elemental bosses"
	quest.3C75FD2842D5A444.title: "Bosses of Mass Destruction"
	quest.3CF2BD950F857013.quest_desc: ["While the others forged metal, the Druid secluded himself in the &2deep woods&r, convinced that the &5Philosopher's Stone&r should not be built, but &acultivated.&r He manipulated the genetics of mystical flowers to the extreme, forcing &eunstable portals&r to &2Alfheim&r and challenging the &aGaia Guardians&r, in an attempt to fuse &2Terrasteel&r with the very soul of nature to grow a &5seed of infinite power&r."]
	quest.3CF2BD950F857013.quest_subtitle: "The Pursuit"
	quest.3CF2BD950F857013.title: "The Druid (Botania)"
	quest.3D24D99C2D136D92.quest_desc: ["Mystical flowers spawn naturally. Use bone meal on any grass to speed it up. You'll need all 16 colors at some point — start collecting now.", "botania:white_mystical_flower", "3D24D99C2D136D92", "481ABF37FF4EBD92", "xp"]
	quest.3D24D99C2D136D92.quest_subtitle: "The first harvest"
	quest.3D24D99C2D136D92.title: "Mystical Flowers"
	quest.3D3B6799C11FA917.quest_desc: ["Here the recipe takes another route: 2× manasteel + 2× prismarine_crystals + 1× §dPure Mana Crystal§r (Pure Mana Crystal) → 1 rune_water.", "", "8000 mana in the runic_altar.", "botania:rune_water", "3D3B6799C11FA917", "07196EF105DEA541", "xp"]
	quest.3D3B6799C11FA917.quest_subtitle: "Cross-mod F3 — elemental rune"
	quest.3D3B6799C11FA917.title: "Rune of Water"
	quest.3D5E79BB273EBCA9.quest_desc: ["Iesnium_ore appears in the nether, only visible with infused_pickaxe or otherworld_goggles. Drops iesnium_dust.", "occultism:iesnium_ore", "3D5E79BB273EBCA9", "16D390CE53E2A2A4", "xp"]
	quest.3D5E79BB273EBCA9.quest_subtitle: "Dimensional ore"
	quest.3D5E79BB273EBCA9.title: "Iesnium Ore"
	quest.3D62C92D16E7A35F.quest_desc: ["Obtain a §6scroll_ice§r and activate it to learn spells from this school.", "", "§7Scrolls are generated in structures, bought from wandering traders, or dropped by mages."]
	quest.3D62C92D16E7A35F.quest_subtitle: "Cone of Cold, Ice Block, Frost Step"
	quest.3D62C92D16E7A35F.title: "School of Ice"
	quest.3D6AEEEDB70DCA28.quest_desc: ["Get §eSalt§r — the base of almost every recipe.", "pamhc2foodcore:saltitem", "3D6AEEEDB70DCA28", "39A4D5E330F75F49", "xp_levels"]
	quest.3D6AEEEDB70DCA28.quest_subtitle: "The basic seasoning"
	quest.3D6AEEEDB70DCA28.title: "Salt"
	quest.3DA8B7FDC6F4365D.quest_desc: ["Steam engine + multi-block boiler with water + heat. An intermediate rotation source — 256+ SU stress capacity.", "create:steam_engine", "3DA8B7FDC6F4365D", "6A77711D3E81DE0E", "xp"]
	quest.3DA8B7FDC6F4365D.quest_subtitle: "Steam-power generation"
	quest.3DA8B7FDC6F4365D.title: "Steam Engine + Boiler"
	quest.3DB142DEEF4E4431.quest_desc: ["The pylon speeds up mana flow around the pool — place four pylons around it and your botanical machines double their pace.", "", "The recipe here includes a §dsource gem§r from the Arcanists — because the pylon channels both magic mana and source at once.", "botania:mana_pylon", "3DB142DEEF4E4431", "3C03596522AA78D3", "xp"]
	quest.3DB142DEEF4E4431.quest_subtitle: "Cross-mod — pool boost"
	quest.3DB142DEEF4E4431.title: "Mana Pylon"
	quest.3DDABD3F2D36F0C9.quest_desc: ["§5Gaia Guardian§r — Botania boss. Summoned with 4 §dGaia Pylons§r + a Beacon in the correct configuration.", "", "Summon it by throwing the §6Gaia Spirit§r into the center of the platform.", "", "§eReward:§r 40 XP levels + Gaia Spirit Ingot"]
	quest.3DDABD3F2D36F0C9.quest_subtitle: "The guardian of the enchanted paradise"
	quest.3DDABD3F2D36F0C9.title: "Slay Gaia Guardian I"
	quest.3E182C9C9E7C7BB4.quest_desc: ["The Engineer's first alloy. Here it requires a §dMagical Agglutinate§r at the center — anyone who hasn't yet walked the Druid's path will need to backtrack.", "", "Without this alloy, no machine takes shape. It's Create's gateway.", "create:andesite_alloy", "3E182C9C9E7C7BB4", "156CC37F81F4B965", "xp"]
	quest.3E182C9C9E7C7BB4.quest_subtitle: "The base alloy of all things Create"
	quest.3E182C9C9E7C7BB4.title: "Andesite Alloy"
	quest.3E368152F33C389C.quest_subtitle: "Giant storage"
	quest.3E368152F33C389C.title: "256k Item Storage Cell"
	quest.3E41341640BA46CE.quest_subtitle: "Top-tier chip"
	quest.3E41341640BA46CE.title: "Engineering Processor"
	quest.3EEF569C7DEC31F5.quest_desc: ["§5Fire Boss§r — a fire elemental boss, in the mod's official §6#forge:bosses§r tag.", "", "Summon via the §6Fire Apothecary§r or spawn in §6Lava Lake structures§r."]
	quest.3EEF569C7DEC31F5.quest_subtitle: "Lord of flames (Apothecarist's Fire Lord)"
	quest.3EEF569C7DEC31F5.title: "Boss: Fire Boss"
	quest.3EF59D574D7CC318.quest_desc: ["There are specific djinni miners (ores, deepslate, nether). Each mines the corresponding blocks in the background. An advanced ore farm.", "occultism:miner_djinni_ores", "3EF59D574D7CC318", "0EDFDE8EEB705973", "xp"]
	quest.3EF59D574D7CC318.quest_subtitle: "Djinni mining"
	quest.3EF59D574D7CC318.title: "Collection of Djinni Miners"
	quest.3EF677CFABA6BA27.quest_desc: ["Mixer + basin processes mixing recipes (brass, andesite alloy refining, source_fluid via EQSMP). Combine with a heater for heated recipes.", "create:mechanical_mixer", "3EF677CFABA6BA27", "45B9E1587A420E2A", "xp"]
	quest.3EF677CFABA6BA27.quest_subtitle: "Mixes liquids/items"
	quest.3EF677CFABA6BA27.title: "Mechanical Mixer"
	quest.3F9E85FD26AD09F9.quest_desc: ["Obtain a §6scroll_lightning§r and activate it to learn spells from this school.", "", "§7Scrolls are generated in structures, bought from wandering traders, or dropped by mages."]
	quest.3F9E85FD26AD09F9.quest_subtitle: "Chain Lightning, Lightning Bolt, Ascension"
	quest.3F9E85FD26AD09F9.title: "School of Lightning"
	quest.3FAE41B505A01BAB.quest_subtitle: "Diagnostics"
	quest.3FAE41B505A01BAB.title: "Network Tool"
	quest.3FD6AB847551AF2D.quest_subtitle: "Connecting everything"
	quest.3FD6AB847551AF2D.title: "Fluix Cable"
	quest.4016BD52970D18B4.quest_desc: ["This §ekey§r opens the §6grave§r that appears where you died.", "", "§7•§r Use it on the grave to release all your items back at once, without picking up piece by piece.", "§7•§r Keep a spare at base: dying far from home without the key is a headache."]
	quest.4016BD52970D18B4.quest_subtitle: "Opens your grave"
	quest.4016BD52970D18B4.title: "Grave Key"
	quest.401F0BFE5F34B95A.quest_desc: ["A large cogwheel + an adjacent small cogwheel change the speed (2× faster with the small driving the large; 0.5× the other way around).", "create:large_cogwheel", "401F0BFE5F34B95A", "192AD440401B1379", "xp"]
