	quest.44FC81F643639B8D.title: "Personal Key"
	quest.45119629535186B4.quest_desc: ["§6Brass Ingot§r is Create's key alloy: melt §6Copper§r and §6Zinc§r together in a heated §6Mixer§r or a foundry furnace.", "", "It's the base material for advanced machinery. Without brass, none of the §eKinetic Core§r ever gets off the ground."]
	quest.45119629535186B4.title: "Brass Ingot"
	quest.45197D26079FD2CC.quest_desc: ["§eBBQ Chicken Pizza§r is an §6advanced dish§r in Pam's.", "", "It brings together dough, chicken, sauce and several ingredients prepared in different utensils.", "A generous reward of hunger and saturation §7•§r for those who master the kitchen."]
