	quest.6451E6E385BCF00A.quest_desc: ["The stone from the other world. It's born when you throw cobblestone into a spirit fire — spirit fire that purifies ordinary stone.", "", "Without otherstone, the Druid can't build his pool. Even those who never want to touch a demonic pact will need to pass through here at least once."]
