	quest.64D174A7341C9E7E.title: "Slay BOMD Lich"
	quest.64DFAC011ACBEF7D.quest_desc: ["The pool is the heart of Botania — where all mana accumulates.", "", "Here it isn't made with plain livingrock: the formula calls for §6otherstone§r, the stone that occultists craft with spirit fire. Without walking the Occultism path, the Druid can't fill his pool."]
