	quest.68B0D48131E4048D.quest_desc: ["Botania's §2Terrasteel§r has been unlocked by the §eSpiritual Core§r.", "", "The sacred metal born on the §aTerrestrial Agglomeration Plate§r — the pinnacle of magical progression, the reward for uniting the four paths."]
