	quest.69889892CC4D2887.quest_desc: ["§6Andesite Alloy§r is Create's mechanical cement: §6Andesite§r + a drop of §6Iron§r or §6Zinc§r in the §6Mixer§r.", "", "It binds nearly every kinetic part together. Combine it with the §6Brass Ingot§r to build the heart of this phase."]
